<div class="content">
  <h1><!-- InstanceBeginEditable name="Title" -->Convening Circular<!-- InstanceEndEditable --></h1>
  <!-- InstanceBeginEditable name="Content" -->
  <p>This convening circular is organized in four sections: Information (yellow);<br />
    Resolutions (pink); Memorials (green) and Reports (blue). </p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong><a href="/gs2007/rr/information/index.htm">Information</a> <br />
    </strong>This   section contains a variety of documents to assist you in your preparations   for General Synod.</li>
  </ul>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="information/gs2007-agenda-draft-08.pdf"><strong>Agenda</strong></a> - Draft agenda for General Synod 2007. </li>
  </ul>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="/gs2007/rr/resolutions/index.htm"><strong>Resolutions</strong></a> <br />
      Resolutions for consideration by General Synod.
      <ul>
        <li>Resolutions   from Committees, Councils, Boards<strong> </strong>and Officers &ldquo;A&rdquo; </li>
        <li> Resolutions   (Memorials) from Ecclesiastical Provinces  and   Dioceses &ldquo;B&rdquo; </li>
        <li> Resolutions   from Members of the General Synod &ldquo;C&rdquo; </li>
      </ul>
    </li>
  </ul>
  <blockquote>
    <p><a href="/gs2007/rr/resolutions/rtc.pdf">Resolution Tally Sheets</a> are included in the Resolutions Section. They are an easy way of recording the decisions of the General Synod. </p>
  </blockquote>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="/gs2007/rr/memorials/index.htm"><strong>Memorials </strong></a><br />
    Memorials to General Synod. </li>
  </ul>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="/gs2007/rr/reports/index.htm"><strong>Reports</strong></a><br /> 
    Reports from Committees and Councils to General Synod.</li>
  </ul>
  <p><strong>Two Important Notices</strong></p>
  <ol start="1" type="1">
    <li><strong>The Handbook</strong></li>
  </ol>
  <p>Two copies of <em>The Handbook of the General Synod of the Anglican Church of Canada</em> will be available at each table. <a href="https://www.anglican.ca/handbook/index.htm">The <em>Handbook </em>is also available online</a>.</p>
  <ol start="2" type="1">
    <li><strong>The Journal of Proceedings</strong></li>
  </ol>
  <p><strong></strong>The <strong>Record of Proceedings, </strong>which members of the General Synod will receive after Synod, will contain <strong>only</strong> the Minutes of the Synod, a list of the Acts of the Synod and a collation of the constitutional and canonical changes enacted by the Synod. The Record will <strong>not</strong> include reports contained in the Convening Circular and the Supplement.</p>
  <p>The <strong>Record of Proceedings </strong>will be provided in a format consistent with that of the Convening Circular, so that, by putting the two together, members will have, in fact, a complete Journal of Proceedings of the Synod.</p>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="/gs2007/rr/Convening-Circular-Organization.pdf">This document in PDF format</a></li>
  </ul>
  <hr />
  
  <h3>Reports of General Synod committees to General Synod:</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="/gs2007/rr/Second Report of the Nominations Committee nodetail.pdf">Second Report of the Second Report of the Nominations Committee - Standing Committees 2007-2010 </a></li>
  </ul>
